OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSchool inspection system   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fneeds more empathy, says   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fnew boss                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The body overseeing school inspections 
OL,6, must listen to the criticism it has    
OL,7, received following the suicide of head 
OL,8, teacher Ruth Perry, its new chief says.
OL,10,FIn his first interview in the job, Sir 
OL,11,FMartyn Oliver said Ofsted had to ensure
OL,12,Fhigh standards in schools - but said it
OL,13,Fcould also be "far more empathetic".   
OL,15,FLast month, a coroner ruled that a     
OL,16,Fcritical report by the organisation    
OL,17,Fcontributed to Mrs Perry's suicide.    
OL,19,FSince the inquest head teachers' unions
OL,20,Fhave demanded a pause to inspections.  
